27#ifndef DH_H
28#define DH_H
29
30struct dhgroup {
31 int size;
32 BIGNUM *g;
33 BIGNUM *p;
34};
35
36DH *choose_dh(int, int, int);
37DH *dh_new_group_asc(const char *, const char *);
38DH *dh_new_group(BIGNUM *, BIGNUM *);
39DH *dh_new_group1(void);
40DH *dh_new_group14(void);
41DH *dh_new_group16(void);
42DH *dh_new_group18(void);
43DH *dh_new_group_fallback(int);
44
45int dh_gen_key(DH *, int);
46int dh_pub_is_valid(const DH *, const BIGNUM *);
47
48u_int dh_estimate(int);
49
50/*
51 * Max value from RFC4419.
52 * Min value from RFC8270.
53 */
54#define DH_GRP_MIN 2048
55#define DH_GRP_MAX 8192
56
57/*
58 * Values for "type" field of moduli(5)
59 * Specifies the internal structure of the prime modulus.
60 */
61#define MODULI_TYPE_UNKNOWN (0)
62#define MODULI_TYPE_UNSTRUCTURED (1)
63#define MODULI_TYPE_SAFE (2)
64#define MODULI_TYPE_SCHNORR (3)
65#define MODULI_TYPE_SOPHIE_GERMAIN (4)
66#define MODULI_TYPE_STRONG (5)
67
68/*
69 * Values for "tests" field of moduli(5)
70 * Specifies the methods used in checking for primality.
71 * Usually, more than one test is used.
72 */
73#define MODULI_TESTS_UNTESTED (0x00)
74#define MODULI_TESTS_COMPOSITE (0x01)
75#define MODULI_TESTS_SIEVE (0x02)
76#define MODULI_TESTS_MILLER_RABIN (0x04)
77#define MODULI_TESTS_JACOBI (0x08)
78#define MODULI_TESTS_ELLIPTIC (0x10)
79
80
81#endif
